sequenceDiagram
    actor Browser
    participant API as Spring Boot
    participant QC as QuestionClassifier

    Browser->>API: question text
    API->>QC: classify(question)

    QC->>QC: Check length — too short or bare word
    alt INVALID
        QC-->>API: earlyReturn — "Could you rephrase?"
        API-->>Browser: message + done
    end

    QC->>QC: Match OUT_OF_SCOPE pattern (weather / news / recipes...)
    alt OUT_OF_SCOPE
        QC-->>API: earlyReturn — "That's outside what I can help with."
        API-->>Browser: message + done
    end

    QC->>QC: Match STRATEGIC pattern (salary / weaknesses / conflict...)
    alt STRATEGIC
        QC-->>API: earlyReturn — "Happy to discuss in our conversation."
        API-->>Browser: message + done
    end

    QC->>QC: Match CONTACT pattern (phone / email / how to contact...)
    alt CONTACT_REDIRECT
        QC-->>API: earlyReturn — "Please download my resume."
        API-->>Browser: message + done
    end

    QC->>QC: Match FACTUAL pattern (how long / when / where are you...)
    alt FACTUAL
        QC-->>API: FACTUAL — strict citation prompt
    end

    QC->>QC: Match BEHAVIORAL_PRE ("Tell me about a time...")
    alt BEHAVIORAL
        QC-->>API: BEHAVIORAL — STAR structure prompt
    end

    QC->>QC: Match TECHNICAL pattern (architecture / Redis / performance...)
    alt TECHNICAL
        QC-->>API: TECHNICAL — explain approach prompt
    end

    QC-->>API: BEHAVIORAL (default)
    API->>API: Continue to retrieval pipeline
